{"tid":2401064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Clubhouse 被封 中国外交部：中国互聯網是開放的","createTime":"2021-02-09T12:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T12:59:37.000Z","uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66a17ff449899439b05e95163d5554da5c510ee7","tid":2401064,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"有記者提問，一個源自美國的語音應用Clubhouse疑似在中國被屏蔽，此前這個應用的用戶數量激增，請問你瞭解為甚麼這個應用會被屏蔽，或者對於它的這個火爆程度有甚麼評論？<br />\n對此發言人回應稱，&quot;我不瞭解你提到的這個具體的情況，作為原則，我想向你闡述兩點。第一，中國的互聯網是開放的，同時中國政府依法依規管理互聯網。第二，中方在有關問題上的立場是一貫明確的，中方捍衛國家主權安全發展利益，反對外部勢力干擾的決心堅定不移&quot;。<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.sputniknews.cn/china/202102091033061743/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.sputniknews.cn%2Fchina%2F202102091033061743%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=9e8e1ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.sputniknews.cn/china/202102091033061743/</a>"},{"pid":"4befb88a7d1306d452ed792107b39cd43c2c653e","tid":2401064,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"笑話部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cb286f973c51bac6d0ed05a5838f08bdae4fbb","tid":2401064,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"講個笑話你聽，中國有民主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/74238376_3465183053522292_6645859950893465600_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=oJe8oLgGXrQAX_d6O9d&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg5-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=29c49c270bd93f9056c1f548ebb33f8f&amp;oe=6046D92D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F74238376_3465183053522292_6645859950893465600_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DoJe8oLgGXrQAX_d6O9d%26_nc_h